<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>byty wbynk frq kbyr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bqlk rby mạ fyy wḥdy bhạlʿạlm kạfḥ trkwny lly ḥwạlyy wnfsy msẖ qạdr sạmḥ
 btqly ạ̉nạ bḥbk kl ạlmạḍy gẖfrtlk
 bʿtlk ạ̹bny ạlwḥyd wrḥ ạ̹bqạ wạqf ḥdk
 ạlqrạr- byny wbynk frq kbyr bạlạ̉ʿmạl wbạltfkyr
 byny wbynk frq kbyr ʿndk lkl sẖy tdbyr
 2- bqlk rby ạlḥml tqyl kyf btkẖṭy ạltjạrb
 kl sẖy ṣạyr mstḥyl ktrt ʿndy ạlmṣạʿb
 btqly ạ̉nạ ḥạḍr ạ̉nạ ạlạ̉wl ạ̉nạ ạlạkẖr
 mʿy lmạ byṣyr byṣyr ʿkl sẖy ạ̉nạ qạdr
 3- bqlk ạ̹ny bkẖạf ktyr mạ bwtẖq bạlmstqbl
 mạ ʿndy ạ̹ymạn kbyr mn qạdr ạ̹tḥml
 btqly ʿṭytk ḥkmh ʿlsạnk syf ạlklmh
 mạ tkwn lkẖwfk ạ̉syr rḥ btkfyk ạlnʿmh</lyrics>
<author>klwd ạ̉by ḥydr, kmạl syqly</author>
<hymn_number>7148</hymn_number>
</song>